PyGoocanvas (Python Bindings for GooCanvas)

GooCanvas is a canvas widget for GTK+ that uses the cairo 2D
library for drawing.  GooCanvas  is similar in many ways  to
GnomeCanvas and FooCanvas,  but it uses cairo for rendering.
PyGoocanvas provides the  Python bindings for GooCanvas.

http://developer.berlios.de/projects/pygoocanvas